44:12.650 --> 44:15.386
Check out our B-rate choreography.

44:31.635 --> 44:32.503
What do you think?

44:34.805 --> 44:36.640
Isn't there anything we can do?

44:37.708 --> 44:40.210
I'll try something easier.

